hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Three years fullyrawkristina In 1983, he declared he wouldn’t go on singing beyond the age of 50 because there were other things he wanted to do. Later, he took up directorships at the Washington National Opera and the Los Angeles Opera, adding a coast-to-coast lifestyle to his air miles. He says he accepted them because he thought he would have to retire and so he would conduct instead. “And here I am, almost 20 years later, and I’m still singing.”
